text:
INDIA VS AUSTRALIA, 4TH TEST Live Cricket Score - India vs Australia, 4th Test, Day 1, Dharamsala Cricbuzz Staff • Last updated on Sat, 25 Mar, 2017, 08:58 AM Australia paid a visit to the Dalai Lama © AFP 
KULDEEP TO DEBUT: — BCCI (@BCCI) March 25, 2017 
KOHLI OUT! 
A brilliant contest, hopefully. The final Test of this long and fascinating season for India. Kohli's shoulder is the subject of speculation. Unfortunately Kohli will be missing out, confirmed India's batting coach Sanjay Bangar. Ajinkya Rahane will be leading the side. 
Toss and teams coming up shortly. © Cricbuzz
